Why Does KMP Work?

Suppose

ababab

Longest Prefix = Longest Suffix

abab

Remaining part

ab

is the repeating unit.

Formula

Repeating Length = n - lastPrefix

If

n % RepeatingLength == 0

then the string consists of repeated copies of that substring.

